node.text:
Ahead of this weekend’s big race, the drivers of the @porsche Motorsport GT Team walk us through their training circuit in Aragon, Spain. With long straights that allow the drivers to reach up to 300kph in speed, the track is the ideal spot to test the unique aerodynamic kit specific for this race.

Check back this weekend to root the team on to victory!

node.text:
What an intense and rich year.
After celebrating 160 years of watchmaking, we look forward to the next 160!
Let’s go back to our biggest moments that made 2020.

node.text:
Forever raising the bar.

A graceful wavy pattern decorating the dial and a unidirectional turning bezel for accurate dive time measurement, the #TAGHeuerAquaracer Professional 300 has all your bases covered. 
Discover more at the link in our bio.

node.text:
Versatility beyond belief.

On or off the court, the #TAGHeuerAquaracer Professional 300 is the watch of choice for tennis superstar @naomiosaka.

Discover more at the link in our bio.

node.text:
Thank you, @PatrickDempsey, for joining us for this iconic race weekend!

We had the privilege to go behind the scenes with Patrick and Alex Stehlig and witness the great work the teams did all weekend. Congratulations to all the teams for a brilliant race!

If you missed it, go in our highlights stories and discover how the race went!

#DontCrackUnderPressure
